{"title_page": "Sam Lowrie", "text_new": "{{Infobox rugby league biography\n|name     = Sam Lowrie\n|fullname       = Samuel Arthur Lowrie<ref>http://www.nzleague.co.nz/players/kiwi_details/138</ref>\n|nickname       = \n|image          = \n|image_size     =\n|caption        =\n|country        =  \n|position       = {{rlp|HK|SR}}\n|birth_date    = \n|birth_place   = New Zealand\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height         =  \n|weight         =  \n|club1          = [[Ponsonby Ponies|Ponsonby]]\n|year1start     = 1914\n|year1end       =  25\n|appearances1   = 149\n|tries1         = 12\n|goals1         = 1\n|fieldgoals1    = 0\n|points1        = 38\n|club2               = \n|year2start          = \n|year2end            = \n|appearances2        = \n|tries2              = \n|goals2              = \n|fieldgoals2         = \n|points2             = \n|teamA          = [[Auckland rugby league team|Auckland]]\n|yearAstart     = 1919\n|yearAend       = 22\n|appearancesA   = 8\n|triesA         = 1\n|goalsA         = 1\n|fieldgoalsA    = 0\n|pointsA        = 5\n|teamB               = [[New Zealand national rugby league team|New Zealand]]\n|yearBstart          = 1919\n|yearBend            = 25\n|appearancesB        = 6\n|triesB              = 0\n|goalsB              = 0\n|fieldgoalsB         = 0\n|pointsB             = 0\n|teamC               = [[New Zealand M\u0101ori rugby league team|New Zealand M\u0101ori]]\n|yearCstart          = 1922\n|yearCend            = \n|appearancesC        = \n|triesC              = \n|goalsC              = \n|fieldgoalsC         = \n|pointsC             = \n|teamD               = \n|yearDstart          = \n|yearDend            = \n|appearancesD        = \n|triesD              = \n|goalsD              = \n|fieldgoalsD         = \n|pointsD             = \n|updated        = \n|source         = <ref name=\"Statistics at rugbyleagueproject.org\">{{cite web|url=http://www.rugbyleagueproject.org/players/Sam-Lowrie/summary.html|title=Statistics at rugbyleagueproject.org|publisher=rugbyleagueproject.org|date=31 December 2017|accessdate=1 January 2018}}</ref>\n|new            = yes\n}}\n\n'''Samuel Arthur \"Sam\" Lowrie''' was a New Zealand [[rugby league]] player who represented [[New Zealand national rugby league team|New Zealand]].<ref name=\"Statistics at rugbyleagueproject.org\"/> His grandnephew, [[Jason Lowrie]], also represented New Zealand in rugby league.\n\n==Playing career==\nLowrie played for the [[Ponsonby Ponies|Ponsonby club]] in the [[Auckland Rugby League]] competition.<ref name=akl100>Coffey, John and Bernie Wood ''Auckland, 100 years of rugby league, 1909-2009'', 2009. {{ISBN|978-1-86969-366-4}}.</ref>\n\nIn 1919 Lowrie played for [[Auckland rugby league team|Auckland]] and was first selected to represent [[New Zealand national rugby league team|New Zealand]], playing in three test matches against the touring [[Australia national rugby league team|Australian side]].\n\nIn 1922 Lowrie toured Australia, with the [[New Zealand M\u0101ori rugby league team]].<ref name=pp7476>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.co.nz/books?id=nklWo8vw-iIC&pg=PA74&lpg=PA74&dq=sam%20lowrie%20rugby%20league&source=bl&ots=tHPqBdzo5i&sig=oQOisPe-k1o9Cn-1lYwNHd4J93c&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjrs7b7y6jNAhWBKaYKHTf5CqAQ6AEIQjAH#v=onepage&q=sam%20lowrie%20rugby%20league&f=false|title=100 Years: M\u0101ori Rugby League, 1908-2008|first1=John Oliver|last1=Coffey|first2=Bernie|last2=Wood|date=1 January 2008|publisher=Huia Publishers|via=Google Books|pages=74\u201376}}</ref>\n\nLowrie was named Ponsonby's best forward in 1923. He again played for New Zealand in 1924, against the touring [[Great Britain Lions]], and toured Australia in 1925, a tour where no test matches were played.\n\nHe retired in 1927 after fracturing his jaw. He played in 149 games for Ponsonby between 1914 and 1927, out of a possible 196.<ref name=pp7476/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Lowrie, Sam}}\n[[Category:New Zealand rugby league players]]\n[[Category:New Zealand national rugby league team players]]\n[[Category:Auckland rugby league team players]]\n[[Category:New Zealand M\u0101ori rugby league team players]]\n[[Category:Ponsonby Ponies players]]\n[[Category:Rugby league hookers]]\n[[Category:Rugby league second-rows]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox rugby league biography\n|name     = Sam Lowrie\n|fullname       = Samuel Arthur Lowrie<ref>http://www.nzleague.co.nz/players/kiwi_details/138</ref>\n|nickname       = \n|image          = \n|image_size     =\n|caption        =\n|country        =  \n|position       = {{rlp|HK|SR}}\n|birth_date    = \n|birth_place   = New Zealand\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height         =  \n|weight         =  \n|club1          = [[Ponsonby Ponies|Ponsonby]]\n|year1start     = 1914\n|year1end       =  24\n|appearances1   = 149\n|tries1         = 11\n|goals1         = 1\n|fieldgoals1    = 0\n|points1        = 35\n|club2               = \n|year2start          = \n|year2end            = \n|appearances2        = \n|tries2              = \n|goals2              = \n|fieldgoals2         = \n|points2             = \n|teamA          = [[Auckland rugby league team|Auckland]]\n|yearAstart     = 1919\n|yearAend       = 22\n|appearancesA   = 8\n|triesA         = 1\n|goalsA         = 1\n|fieldgoalsA    = 0\n|pointsA        = 5\n|teamB               = [[New Zealand national rugby league team|New Zealand]]\n|yearBstart          = 1919\n|yearBend            = 25\n|appearancesB        = 6\n|triesB              = 0\n|goalsB              = 0\n|fieldgoalsB         = 0\n|pointsB             = 0\n|teamC               = [[New Zealand M\u0101ori rugby league team|New Zealand M\u0101ori]]\n|yearCstart          = 1922\n|yearCend            = \n|appearancesC        = \n|triesC              = \n|goalsC              = \n|fieldgoalsC         = \n|pointsC             = \n|teamD               = \n|yearDstart          = \n|yearDend            = \n|appearancesD        = \n|triesD              = \n|goalsD              = \n|fieldgoalsD         = \n|pointsD             = \n|updated        = \n|source         = <ref name=\"Statistics at rugbyleagueproject.org\">{{cite web|url=http://www.rugbyleagueproject.org/players/Sam-Lowrie/summary.html|title=Statistics at rugbyleagueproject.org|publisher=rugbyleagueproject.org|date=31 December 2017|accessdate=1 January 2018}}</ref>\n|new            = yes\n}}\n\n'''Samuel Arthur \"Sam\" Lowrie''' was a New Zealand [[rugby league]] player who represented [[New Zealand national rugby league team|New Zealand]].<ref name=\"Statistics at rugbyleagueproject.org\"/> His grandnephew, [[Jason Lowrie]], also represented New Zealand in rugby league.\n\n==Playing career==\nLowrie played for the [[Ponsonby Ponies|Ponsonby club]] in the [[Auckland Rugby League]] competition.<ref name=akl100>Coffey, John and Bernie Wood ''Auckland, 100 years of rugby league, 1909-2009'', 2009. {{ISBN|978-1-86969-366-4}}.</ref>\n\nIn 1919 Lowrie played for [[Auckland rugby league team|Auckland]] and was first selected to represent [[New Zealand national rugby league team|New Zealand]], playing in three test matches against the touring [[Australia national rugby league team|Australian side]].\n\nIn 1922 Lowrie toured Australia, with the [[New Zealand M\u0101ori rugby league team]].<ref name=pp7476>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.co.nz/books?id=nklWo8vw-iIC&pg=PA74&lpg=PA74&dq=sam%20lowrie%20rugby%20league&source=bl&ots=tHPqBdzo5i&sig=oQOisPe-k1o9Cn-1lYwNHd4J93c&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjrs7b7y6jNAhWBKaYKHTf5CqAQ6AEIQjAH#v=onepage&q=sam%20lowrie%20rugby%20league&f=false|title=100 Years: M\u0101ori Rugby League, 1908-2008|first1=John Oliver|last1=Coffey|first2=Bernie|last2=Wood|date=1 January 2008|publisher=Huia Publishers|via=Google Books|pages=74\u201376}}</ref>\n\nLowrie was named Ponsonby's best forward in 1923. He again played for New Zealand in 1924, against the touring [[Great Britain Lions]], and toured Australia in 1925, a tour where no test matches were played.\n\nHe retired in 1927 after fracturing his jaw. He played in 149 games for Ponsonby between 1914 and 1927, out of a possible 196.<ref name=pp7476/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Lowrie, Sam}}\n[[Category:New Zealand rugby league players]]\n[[Category:New Zealand national rugby league team players]]\n[[Category:Auckland rugby league team players]]\n[[Category:New Zealand M\u0101ori rugby league team players]]\n[[Category:Ponsonby Ponies players]]\n[[Category:Rugby league hookers]]\n[[Category:Rugby league second-rows]]\n", "name_user": "Yamis", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sam_Lowrie"}
